Package: rags2ridges
Type: Package
Title: Ridge Estimation of Precision Matrices from High-Dimensional Data
Version: 2.2.3
Maintainer: Carel F.W. Peeters <cf.peeters@vumc.nl>
Author: Carel F.W. Peeters [cre, aut], Anders Ellern Bilgrau [aut], Wessel N. van Wieringen [aut]
Description: Proper L2-penalized maximum likelihood estimators for 
  precision matrices and supporting functions to employ these estimators
  in a graphical modeling setting.
Depends: R (>= 2.15.1)
biocViews:
Imports: igraph, stats, methods, expm, reshape, ggplot2, Hmisc, fdrtool, 
  snowfall, sfsmisc, utils, grDevices, graphics, gRbase, RBGL, graph, 
  Rcpp, RSpectra
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
KeepSource: yes
